&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Village at Rockville – Where Drivers Make Every Journey Safe and Enjoyable!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title:&lt;/strong&gt; Driver&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Type:&lt;/strong&gt; PRN / As Needed&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pay Range:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;$19.50 - $23.75/hour &lt;em&gt;(Final offer based on your unique skills, experience)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At The Village at Rockville, a National Lutheran Community, every ride is more than a trip—it’s a chance to make someone’s day brighter. Our team takes pride in providing safe, friendly, and dependable transportation that helps residents stay active, engaged, and connected. We’re looking for a caring and dependable Driver to join us in supporting a community where every journey matters.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why You&#39;ll LOVE Working with Us&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Essential Team Member:&amp;nbsp;Safely transport residents to appointments, activities, and outings, making every trip comfortable and enjoyable.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Positive Atmosphere:&amp;nbsp;Be part of a supportive, upbeat team that values respect, reliability, and service.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make a Difference:&amp;nbsp;Your friendly attitude and attention to safety help residents maintain independence and stay engaged.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible Schedule: Enjoy the flexibility of part-time work, with shifts that fit your availability and lifestyle.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You&#39;ll Do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Responsible for transporting residents safely and professionally to all scheduled destinations, appointments, and shopping trips; no unscheduled stops&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keeps vehicles and equipment maintained and stocked with necessary supplies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensures vehicles receive documented routine maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintains vehicles in clean condition inside and out, including regular washing, vacuuming, and window cleaning&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintains accurate vehicle mileage and trip logs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Performs other duties as required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We&#39;re Looking For&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;CDL&#39;s with passenger endorsement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Clean driving record&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Friendly, patient, and courteous demeanor who is customer focused&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to assist residents in and out of vehicles as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Interpersonal&amp;nbsp;Skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity&amp;nbsp;with&amp;nbsp;Vehicle&amp;nbsp;Maintenance&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Commercial&amp;nbsp;Passenger&amp;nbsp;Bus&amp;nbsp;License&amp;nbsp;a&amp;nbsp;plus!&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At The Village at Rockville, you’re more than a driver—you’re a trusted companion, a friendly face, and an essential part of making every day extraordinary for our residents.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Apply today and join a community that values YOU!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

