&lt;li&gt;Ensures identified deficiencies are promptly corrected&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support and guide the EVS team to deliver seamless, high-quality cleaning and sanitation for all residents, employees, and guests.&lt;/li&gt;
